Preliminary questions for analysis derived but expanding on the IALSA grant application:

1) How do we best characterize retirement for analysts interested in understanding aging? (What is important about retirement for aging researchers?)

2) What is the role of (direct and indirect) selection in the association between retirement and aging? (Are those who retire different from those who can/do not?)

3) How are the effects of retirement and unemployment similar or different? (Is it really just lack of formal activity?)

4) What characteristics mediate the association between retirement and aging? (What does healthy retirement look like?)

...

